· Construction of 100-meter test track
· Validation of levitation and acceleration
· Launch of 1 kg test masses

Phase 2: Initial Operational Capability (Years 5-7)

· 1,000-meter track extension
· SMES installation (1 GJ capacity)
· First 100 kg operational payloads

Phase 3: Full Scale (Years 8-10)

· Completion to 3,200 meters
· Full power system (4 GJ SMES)
· 1,000 kg operational capability

