10.4 The Engineering Legacy

Project Slingstone represents more than a transportation system; it is an exercise in extreme systems engineering that will advance multiple disciplines:

· High-field superconductivity at scale
· Gigawatt-scale pulsed power
· Autonomous construction in remote environments
· Precision orbital mechanics
· Sustainable off-world industrialization

The technical foundations presented here provide a rigorous starting point for humanity's transformation of the Moon from a destination into a departure point for the Solar System.

